          <text>by striking <quote>and</quote> at the end of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1612/ss:b/p:25">paragraph (25)</cato:entity-ref>;</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H53E7708050BE4E1A851E8197FF0AEA91">
