          <text>by adding at the end the following:</text>
					<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H40F01FDA9DC14FD08BE5F2DF8B31C144" style="OLC">
						<paragraph id="HD71F71E9936D461FA4AEDF9F9C08113C">
